{"tid":1507004,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【終極一戰】9.30 全港罷工罷課搲春袋","createTime":"2019-08-26T03:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T13:51:20.000Z","uid":273852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"973800377387a6292c253aeaa80084b5d5f396d5","tid":1507004,"uid":273852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:51:04.000Z","msg":"[P牌出Post]<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">鄰國牛一前</span>賀一賀佢 (有人話牛一前要完事? 天真)<br />\n- 罷完<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第2日「<span style=\"color: red;\">紅日</span>」繼續賀</span> (佢會唔會牛一出老解先?)<br />\n- 咁多人罷，冇嘢做，最好當然係去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">搲春袋</span><br />\n- 唔駛去到春袋咁遠，去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">通往春袋嘅鳩毛</span>就得，有人出人，有車出車<br />\n- 人傳人搵仲有良知嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">巴士佬/黨鐵佬/空姐</span>一齊罷 (佢地仲未撚肯罷! 冇撚用!)<br />\n- 就算罷完又係冇回應 (9成9)，就係要佢樣衰，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">樣衰俾全世界睇</span><br />\n- 如果吹得夠行，佢唔想牛一樣衰，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">迫佢之前有所讓步</span><br />\n- 全球登報，呼籲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全地球港人</span>9.30一齊罷工罷課<br />\n- <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10.1唔駛俾$</span>全球登報，若然我哋成功，就自然免費上報<br />\n- 由而家到9.30前，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全由和理非keep住行，勇武休養生息兵一個月</span>，齋和理非行佢冇得「牛一前完事」<br />\n- <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">罷一放四</span>，鳩假期誠意推介<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>五大訴求 缺一不可</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c7bfe3748a12be37d644ac2f0616c5e312d0b47b","tid":1507004,"uid":273852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:54:54.000Z","msg":"P牌自推100次"},{"pid":"36e341f462be2ddd33b4dbbcebd9455f91aeaa89","tid":150700